{"title":"新绝句（五首）","authors":["莫少云"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":4,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新绝句（五首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫少云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友人蓦然来访"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带他乡风景他乡人情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与我同度今夜良宵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品陈酒一杯之醇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季追寻阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呐喊出新的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围一圈城廓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝固一年的欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌纹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河之曲折"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江之委婉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于掌中交错成绝唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘溢出母亲沉吟的音符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前头他乡酒后头故园愁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两头加添同样时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担子越来越向故园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子是失去平衡的挑夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀古"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉思于传说的古迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽烟由眼前飞逝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛觉山岳齐在崛起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬铮铮是民族脊梁"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}